   255	3. Reference Python OPEN gate needs `python3.11` with `pyarrow`, `pandas`, `numpy`, `pynumpress`, `psims`.
   256	   Install the latter two if absent: `python3.11 -m pip install pynumpress psims`. Force `import numpy.typing`
   257	   before `from mzpeak import MzPeakFile` (older numpy build does not auto-load the typing submodule).
   258	</build_runtime_setup>
   259	
