   289	2. Dispatch instantiates MzPeakSpectrumWriter; conversion completes without error. [CLI-03]
   290	3. Parquet.Net low-level nested struct + list-of-struct + parallel nullable top-level columns round-trip
   291	   read confirms values. [PQ-01]
   292	4. Reusable PARAM value-struct builder + CV-accession column-name helper exist in a shared support file. [PQ-02]
   293	5. Archive is STORED ZIP with ZSTD-internal Parquet; reference Python reader OPENs it. [PQ-03]
   294	</success_criteria>
